data.description: Spacious country club home that offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and 2 car garage with one side featuring RV height door.  This home has had all the big upgrades completed!  Fully remodeled kitchen, new roof, brand new air conditioner & furnace, 2 new water heaters, and both garage doors are brand new.  So many big upgrades are completed and ready for you to make this your home.  Inside the living room features vaulted ceilings with a fireplace, a new dining room area, and lots of storage.  Enjoy the mountain views from your private backyard!
